This example is a simple H-burn for constant T and rho starting with
solar composition.

# compile
$ make distclean
$ make

# run
$ ./ppn.exe

# make plots
$ ./plot.sh

If you have moved this example dir out of the svn tree you may
have to edit the PCD variable in the Makefile.

Last update:

# fh 151205
     > adapting this example to build update performed by Sam in Dec
       2015
     > updating plotting scripts.